{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2020-02-20-rn-react-navigation5-android-keep-stopping/","result":{"data":{"site":{"id":"Site","siteMetadata":{"title":"Will Lai - Programming!","siteUrl":"https://willlaiwk.github.io"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"103d3381-33f7-5782-9b77-ce95e84f269d","excerpt":"一陣子沒碰 React Native，最近看到 react-navigation 已經進版到了 5.x，所以就參考了官方文件，並在 ios 與 android 模擬器上運行了一下，接著就撞牆了。 Android App 持續出現 keeps stopping 跑在 ios 上完全沒出錯，可是跑在 android…","html":"<p>一陣子沒碰 <a href=\"https://reactnative.dev/\">React Native</a>，最近看到 <a href=\"https://reactnavigation.org/en/\">react-navigation</a> 已經進版到了 5.x，所以就參考了官方文件，並在 ios 與 android 模擬器上運行了一下，接著就撞牆了。</p>\n<h2>Android App 持續出現 keeps stopping</h2>\n<p>跑在 ios 上完全沒出錯，可是跑在 android 卻無法正常開啟 App，如下圖。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 782px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1064fae3c2b8a06a5dc2d4ca1d5840dc/22bc6/p1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 87.21227621483375%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Chinese Salty Egg\"\n        title=\"Chinese Salty Egg\"\n        src=\"/static/1064fae3c2b8a06a5dc2d4ca1d5840dc/22bc6/p1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1064fae3c2b8a06a5dc2d4ca1d5840dc/e07e9/p1.jpg 200w,\n/static/1064fae3c2b8a06a5dc2d4ca1d5840dc/066f9/p1.jpg 400w,\n/static/1064fae3c2b8a06a5dc2d4ca1d5840dc/22bc6/p1.jpg 782w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 782px) 100vw, 782px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>開始除錯</h2>\n<p>為了要知道發生什麼事，我在終端機(Terminal) 執行以下指令，查看模擬器的 log：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">$ adb logcat *:E</code></pre></div>\n<p>這邊顯示的是 log 結果：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">...\n02-19 22:11:00.215  5550  5587 E AndroidRuntime: FATAL EXCEPTION: mqt_native_modules\n02-19 22:11:00.215  5550  5587 E AndroidRuntime: Process: com.tsreactnativedemo, PID: 5550\n02-19 22:11:00.215  5550  5587 E AndroidRuntime: java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: Failed resolution of: Landroidx/swiperefreshlayout/widget/SwipeRefreshLayout;\n...</code></pre></div>\n<p>我用上面 log 中第三段出現的 <code class=\"language-text\">java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError</code> 這段錯誤訊息內容去尋找資料，發現問題是在 <a href=\"https://github.com/software-mansion/react-native-screens\">react-native-screens</a> 這個套件。</p>\n<h2>react-native-screens</h2>\n<p>這個套件目的是暴露 native 的 navigation 容器組件給 React Native 做使用。而 react-navigation 也相依於此，所以在 react-navigation 官方文件也說明要安裝此套件。</p>\n<p>在 react-native-screens 的文件中寫到要在 <code class=\"language-text\">android/app/build.gradle</code> 中的 <code class=\"language-text\">dependencies</code> 區塊加入下面這段:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"groovy\"><pre class=\"language-groovy\"><code class=\"language-groovy\">implementation <span class=\"token string\">'androidx.appcompat:appcompat:1.1.0-rc01'</span>\nimplementation <span class=\"token string\">'androidx.swiperefreshlayout:swiperefreshlayout:1.1.0-alpha02'</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>加入後的完整的程式碼:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"groovy\"><pre class=\"language-groovy\"><code class=\"language-groovy\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">...</span>\ndependencies <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    implementation <span class=\"token function\">fileTree</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>dir<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string gstring\">\"libs\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> include<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string gstring\">\"*.jar\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    implementation <span class=\"token string gstring\">\"com.facebook.react:react-native:+\"</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// From node_modules</span>\n    implementation <span class=\"token string\">'androidx.appcompat:appcompat:1.1.0-rc01'</span>\n    implementation <span class=\"token string\">'androidx.swiperefreshlayout:swiperefreshlayout:1.1.0-alpha02'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>enableHermes<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> hermesPath <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string gstring\">\"../../node_modules/hermes-engine/android/\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        debugImplementation <span class=\"token function\">files</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>hermesPath <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string gstring\">\"hermes-debug.aar\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        releaseImplementation <span class=\"token function\">files</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>hermesPath <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string gstring\">\"hermes-release.aar\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        implementation jscFlavor\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">...</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>成功執行</h2>\n<p>在加入上面那段 code 後，就能順利在 Android 上執行了。</p>\n<h2>後記</h2>\n<p>解決問題的當天我回去看了 React Navigation 4.x 的文件，發現裡面有寫到 react-native-screens 的這段，但 React Navigation 5.x 的文件沒寫到。\n而當我寫這篇文章時，React Navigation 5.x 的文件突然就加上了…，如果我晚點嘗試，是不是就不用踩這個坑了 XD…</p>\n<p>下圖左邊是踩坑當天的文件，右邊是寫這篇文章時的文件…，右邊已補上 react-native-screens 的那段(紅色框框)。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f0cb500b9475f83e3d0fd5ef2bb12aa5/7ebf9/p2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.80510682647212%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Chinese Salty Egg\"\n        title=\"Chinese Salty Egg\"\n        src=\"/static/f0cb500b9475f83e3d0fd5ef2bb12aa5/5a190/p2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f0cb500b9475f83e3d0fd5ef2bb12aa5/772e8/p2.png 200w,\n/static/f0cb500b9475f83e3d0fd5ef2bb12aa5/e17e5/p2.png 400w,\n/static/f0cb500b9475f83e3d0fd5ef2bb12aa5/5a190/p2.png 800w,\n/static/f0cb500b9475f83e3d0fd5ef2bb12aa5/c1b63/p2.png 1200w,\n/static/f0cb500b9475f83e3d0fd5ef2bb12aa5/29007/p2.png 1600w,\n/static/f0cb500b9475f83e3d0fd5ef2bb12aa5/7ebf9/p2.png 1919w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"React Navigation 5.x 踩坑! Android keeps stopping 問題","date":"February 20, 2020","description":"一陣子沒碰 React Native，最近看到 react-navigation 已經進版到了 5.x，所以就參考了官方文件，並在 ios 與 android 模擬器上運行了一下，接著就撞牆了..."}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2020-02-20-rn-react-navigation5-android-keep-stopping/","previous":null,"next":null}}}